OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FThames Water has agreed to pay just
OL,7,F#24.5 million of its record #122.7
OL,8,Fmillion in fines by the end of
OL,9,FSeptember, following negotiations with
OL,10,Fregulator Ofwat.
OL,12,FThe company, which is facing financial
OL,13,Fdifficulties, was handed the penalties
OL,14,Fby the watchdog in May for failures
OL,15,Fover sewage treatment and paying out
OL,16,Fdividends.
OL,18,FA fifth of the fines will be due in an
OL,19,Finitial instalment next month. Thames
OL,20,FWater said the fines would not be paid
OL,21,Fout of customer bills.
