OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FThe remaining 80% is dependent on the
OL,7,Ffinancial security and future of the
OL,8,Fdebt-laden water supplier as it
OL,9,Fteeters on the brink of a possible
OL,10,Ftemporary nationalisation.
OL,12,FOfwat said the remainder will be paid
OL,13,Feither 30 calendar days after it
OL,14,Fsecures a rescue financing deal and
OL,15,Fthere is enough cash liquidity in the
OL,16,Fbusiness or, if it is placed into a
OL,17,Fspecial administration regime by the
OL,18,FGovernment, 30 calendar days after it
OL,19,Fexits the insolvency process.
