OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FOfwat said it had set a final
OL,7,F"backstop date" of March 31 2030 for
OL,8,Fthe remaining penalties.
OL,10,FThe fines were originally due to be
OL,11,Fpaid by August 20, but Thames Water
OL,12,Frequested a payment plan due to its
OL,13,Ffinancial difficulties.
OL,15,FLynn Parker, senior director of
OL,16,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "This
OL,17,Fpayment plan continues to hold Thames
OL,18,FWater to account for their failures
OL,19,Fbut also recognises the ongoing equity
OL,20,Fraise and recapitalisation process.
