OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,F"Our focus remains on ensuring that
OL,7,Fthe company takes the right steps to
OL,8,Fdeliver a turnaround in its
OL,9,Foperational performance and strengthen
OL,10,Fits financial resilience to the
OL,11,Fbenefit of customers."
OL,13,FOfwat announced the fines in May after
OL,14,Fit said an investigation into Thames
OL,15,FWater's sewage treatment works found
OL,16,F"a series of failures by the company
OL,17,Fto build, maintain and operate
OL,18,Fadequate infrastructure".
