OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FThe utility giant was ordered to pay
OL,7,F#104.5 million for the sewage probe,
OL,8,Fplus #18.2 million for breaking rules
OL,9,Fover dividend payments, the industry's
OL,10,Ffirst dividend-related fine.
OL,12,FOfwat pointed to nearly #170 million
OL,13,Fworth of dividend payments by Thames
OL,14,Fin October 2023 and March 2024, which
OL,15,Fthe watchdog said were not justified.
