OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FBut the fines come at a time when
OL,7,FThames is already under extreme
OL,8,Ffinancial stress and its chief
OL,9,Fexecutive Chris Weston has previously
OL,10,Ftold MPs that if the company faced
OL,11,Ffines that were too high, it would
OL,12,Fstruggle to get new investment.
OL,14,FThames Water is feared to be edging
OL,15,Fcloser to a potential temporary
OL,16,Fnationalisation after the Government
OL,17,Fappointed insolvency specialists FTI
OL,18,FConsulting earlier this month to step
OL,19,Fup contingency planning in case the
OL,20,Fsupplier collapses.
