OL,3,CThames Water negotiates payment plan
OL,4,Cfollowing record fine
OL,6,FThese plans could see Britain's
OL,7,Fbiggest water firm placed into a
OL,8,Fspecial administration regime (SAR),
OL,9,Fmeaning it would be put into an
OL,10,Finsolvency process.
OL,12,FThames Water, which has 16 million
OL,13,Fcustomers, remains locked in talks
OL,14,Fover a rescue funding deal with a
OL,15,Fnumber of senior creditors.
OL,17,FBut it recently raised doubts over
OL,18,Fwhether the creditors' refinancing and
OL,19,Frestructuring plans could be
OL,20,Fcompleted, which could ultimately
OL,21,Fresult in a state rescue deal.
